### Assets - REST Client requests

### Get portfolio (requires Bearer token)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/assets/portfolio
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get token balance (requires Bearer token)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/assets/balance/{{symbol}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List tokens (public)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/assets/tokens

### Get token price (public)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/assets/tokens/{{symbol}}/price

### Top holders (public, optional ?limit=)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/assets/tokens/{{symbol}}/holders?limit={{limit}}

### Network stats (public)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/assets/stats/network

### Curl examples

# Get portfolio (curl)
# curl -H "Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>" {{base}}/api/v1/assets/portfolio

# Get balance (curl)
# curl -H "Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>" {{base}}/api/v1/assets/balance/{{symbol}}

# List tokens
# curl {{base}}/api/v1/assets/tokens

# Token price
# curl {{base}}/api/v1/assets/tokens/{{symbol}}/price

# Top holders with limit
# curl "{{base}}/api/v1/assets/tokens/{{symbol}}/holders?limit=5"
